 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Hi-C Diff\n",
    "\n",
    "Draw the difference between two Hi-C contact matrices."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import coolbox\n",
    "from coolbox.api import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "'0.2.5'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "coolbox.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = \"/home/nanguage/Dropbox/workspace/THP_paper/data/cool\"\n",
    "cl1 = f\"{data_dir}/THPP.cool\"\n",
    "cl2 = f\"{data_dir}/Ra.cool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "region = \"chr1:89237500-90307500\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Normalize with `expect` matrix (decay along diagonal), difference with `diff` (matrix_A - matrix_B):"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x794.551 with 18 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl1, style='window') + MinValue(5e-4) + MaxValue(1e-1) + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl2, style='window') + MinValue(5e-4) + MaxValue(1e-1) + \\\n",
    "    HiCDiff(cl1, cl2, style='window', normalize='expect', diff_method='diff') + \\\n",
    "    MinValue(-5) + MaxValue(5) + \\\n",
    "    XAxis()\n",
    "frame *= Feature('depth_ratio', 0.35)\n",
    "frame.plot(region)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### CLI code"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "\n",
    "data_dir=\"/home/nanguage/Dropbox/workspace/THP_paper/data/cool\"\n",
    "cl1=\"${data_dir}/THPP.cool\"\n",
    "cl2=\"${data_dir}/Ra.cool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "coolbox add XAxis - \\\n",
    "start_with Feature \"depth_ratio\" \"0.35\" - \\\n",
    "    start_with MinValue \"5e-4\" - \\\n",
    "    start_with MaxValue \"1e-1\" - \\\n",
    "        add Cool $cl1 --style 'window' - \\\n",
    "        add Cool $cl2 --style 'window' - \\\n",
    "    end_with - \\\n",
    "    end_with - \\\n",
    "    add HiCDiff $cl1 $cl2 --style 'window' --normalize 'expect' --diff_method 'diff' - \\\n",
    "    add MinValue \"-5\" - \\\n",
    "    add MaxValue \"5\" - \\\n",
    "end_with - \\\n",
    "add XAxis - \\\n",
    "goto \"chr1:89237500-90307500\" - \\\n",
    "plot /tmp/test_coolbox.png"
   ]
  }
 ],
